lass=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> File virtualhost app.kreasiacademy.com.conf</h4><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">upstream odookacserver {\n     server 127.0.0.1:8113;\n }\n\n server {\n\n     listen [::]:80;\n     listen 80;\n\n     server_name app.kreasiacademy.com;\n \n\n}\n\n server {\n     listen [::]:443 ssl http2;\n     listen 443 ssl http2;\n\n     server_name app.kreasiacademy.com;\n\n     access_log /var/log/nginx/odoo_access.log;\n     error_log /var/log/nginx/odoo_error.log;\n\n     proxy_read_timeout 720s;\n     proxy_connect_timeout 720s;\n     proxy_send_timeout 720s;\n     proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Host $host;\n     proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n     proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n     proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n\n     location / {\n        proxy_redirect off;\n        proxy_pass http://odookacserver;\n     }\n\n     location ~* /web/static/ {\n         proxy_cache_valid 200 90m;\n         proxy_buffering on;\n         expires 864000;\n         proxy_pass http://odookacserver;\n     }\n\n     gzip_types text/css text/less text/plain text/xml application/xml application/json application/javascript;\n     gzip on;\n \n}\n</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"enabling-virtualhost-3\"><a href=\"#enabling-virtualhost-3\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> Enabling virtualhost</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/app.kreasiacademy.com.conf /et/nginx/sites-enabled/\nsystemctl restart nginx</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Karena domain belum tersedia, maka app.kreasiacademy.com <strong>belum bisa diakses</strong> menggunakan domain.</p><div>\n</div>','[{\"title\":\"Odoo\",\"anchor\":\"#odoo\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"A. Menyiapkan environment dan packages odoo\",\"anchor\":\"#a-menyiapkan-environment-dan-packages-odoo\",\"children\":[{\"title\"