\",\"anchor\":\"#konfigurasi-webserver-dan-app\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"Konfigurasi NGINX Webserver\",\"anchor\":\"#konfigurasi-nginx-webserver\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Konfigurasi SSL Let\'s Encrypt\",\"anchor\":\"#konfigurasi-ssl-lets-encrypt\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Konfigurasi Base URL di Ibiznis App\",\"anchor\":\"#konfigurasi-base-url-di-ibiznis-app\",\"children\":[]}]}]}]','html','2021-08-31T09:15:50.708Z','2021-09-13T04:09:12.710Z','ckeditor','en',3,1,'{\"js\":\"\",\"css\":\"\"}'),(5,'wordpress','785b3c6a55feeb18519d6a0f1f78a5604d8883bc','Wordpress KAT','Akses Wordpress KAT',0,1,NULL,'','','<h1>Akses Wordpress KAT</h1>\n<figure class=\"table\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"4\">\n          <p style=\"text-align:center;\">FTP</p>\n        </td>\n        <td colspan=\"2\">\n          <p style=\"text-align:center;\">Wordpress Login</p>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>No&nbsp;</td>\n        <td>Website</td>\n        <td>User</td>\n        <td>Password</td>\n        <td>User</td>\n        <td>Password</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>odooware.com</td>\n        <td>odooware_lp</td>\n        <td>kreasi123*</td>\n        <td>admin</td>\n        <td>Kreasi123*</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>kreasialamteknologi.com</td>\n        <td>kat_web</td>\n        <td>kreasi123*</td>\n        <td>admin</td>\n        <td>Kreasi123*</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>greenholespace.co.id</td>\n        <td>greenholespace_lp</td>\n        <td>kreasi123*</td>\n        <td>admin</td>\n        <td>admin_greenholespace</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>4</td>\n        <td>ibiznis.id</td>\n        <td>ibiznis_lp</td>\n        <td>kreasi123*</td>\n        <td>admin</td>\n        <td>admin_ibiznis</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</figure>\n<h1>Requirement</h1>\n<ol>\n  <li>PHP</li>\n  <li>NGINX atau Apache Webserver</li>\n  <li>MariaDB</li>\n  <li>Certbot</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>Deploy Wordpress</h1>\n<p>Masuk ke VPS yang akan di deploy wordpress</p>\n<p>Masuk ke direktori untuk mem-<i>publish </i>wordpress</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/html/</code></pre>\n<p>Buat direktori untuk menyimpan file wordpress</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">mkdir nama_website_wordpress/</code></pre>\n<p>Masuk ke direktori</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd nama_website_wordpress/</code></pre>\n<p>Inisialisasi git</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin url_git_repository</code></pre>\n<p>Deploy file di git repositori</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo git fetch --all\nsudo git merge origin/branch_wordpress</code></pre>\n<p>Beri hak akses ke direktori</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">chmod 777 -R /var/www/html/nama_website_wordpress/</code></pre>\n<h1>List Virtualhost Wordpress Website</h1>\n<figure class=\"table\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>No</td>\n        <td>Website</td>\n        <td>Virtualhost Path</td>\n        <td>Wordpress File Path</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>https://kreasialamteknologi.com</td>\n        <td>/etc/nginx/sites-available/kreasialamteknologi.conf</td>\n        <td>/var/www/html/kreasialamteknologi_web/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>https://odooware.com</td>\n        <td>/etc/nginx/sites-available/odooware.conf</td>\n        <td>/var/www/html/odooware_web/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>https://greenholespace.co.id</td>\n        <td>/etc/nginx/sites-available/greenholespace.conf</td>\n        <td>/var/www/html/greenholespace_landingpage/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>4</td>\n        <td>https://ibiznis.id</td>\n        <td>/etc/nginx/sites-available/ibiznis.conf</td>\n        <td>/var/www/html/ibiznis_landingpage/</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</figure>\n<h1>Konfigurasi NGINX Webserver</h1>\n<p>Masuk ke direktori NGINX</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /etc/nginx/sites-available/</code></pre>\n<p>Buat file virtualhost</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano nama_website.conf</code></pre>\n<p>File virtualhost</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">server {\n	listen 80;\n	listen [::]:80;\n\n	server_name nama_website;\n\n	root /path/to/wordpress/directory;\n	# Add index.php to the list if you are using PHP\n    index index.php index.html;\n\n	location / {\n		try_files $uri $uri/ /index.php?$args;\n	}\n}</code></pre>\n<p>Simpan dan buat linkfile ke sites-enable agar bisa diakses melalui browser</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/nama_website.conf /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/</code></pre>\n<p>Restart NGINX</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo systemctl restart nginx</code></pre>\n<h1>Memasang let\'s encrypt SSL</h1>\n<p>Certbot sudah terinstall dengan plugin NGINX, masukan perintah di layar SSH</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo certbot --nginx -d nama_website</code></pre>\n<p>Tunggu hingga certbot selesai <i>enabling </i>SSL untuk website</p>\n<p>Jika ada pilihan untuk <i>redirect, </i>pilih nomer 2 atau <i>redirect</i>. Bertujuan untuk secara otomatis akan mengupdate konfigurasi virtualhost. Redirect langsung ke HTTPS ketika mengakses di browser dengan HTTP.</p>\n<h1>List Database Wordpress</h1>\n<figure class=\"table\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>No</td>\n        <td>Website</td>\n        <td>Database Name</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>https://kreasialamteknologi.com</td>\n        <td>kreasialamteknologi_web</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>https://odooware.com</td>\n        <td>odooware_web</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>https://greenholespace.co.id</td>\n        <td>greenholespace_web</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        