     <tr>\r\n        <td>Database Name</td>\r\n        <td>wiki</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>Dump SQL Path</td>\r\n        <td>/var/www/wiki/db/</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n  </table>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h2>Menambah Database Wiki</h2>\r\n<p>Akses ssh database wiki, kemudian masuk ke mariaDB</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mysql -h 103.152.118.42 -uroot -pKreasi123*</code></pre>\r\n<p>Buat database wiki</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">create database wiki;</code></pre>\r\n<p>Keluar dari mariaDB</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">exit</code></pre>\r\n<h1>Konfigurasi Wiki</h1>\r\n<p>Ganti nama file config.yml</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">mv config.sample.yml config.yml</code></pre>\r\n<p>Edit konfigurasi wiki</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">nano config.yml</code></pre>\r\n<p>Konfigurasi wiki, edit bagian port dan database wiki yang telah dibuat.</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\"># ---------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n# Port the server should listen to\r\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nport: 3300 \r\n\r\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n# Database\r\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n# Supported Database Engines:\r\n# - postgres = PostgreSQL 9.5 or later\r\n# - mysql = MySQL 8.0 or later (5.7.8 partially supported, refer to docs)\r\n# - mariadb = MariaDB 10.2.7 or later\r\n# - mssql = MS SQL Server 2012 or later\r\n# - sqlite = SQLite 3.9 or later\r\n\r\ndb:\r\n  type: mariadb\r\n\r\n  # PostgreSQL / MySQL / MariaDB / MS SQL Server only:\r\n  host: localhost\r\n  port: 3306\r\n  user: root\r\n  pass: Kreasi123*\r\n  db: wiki\r\n  ssl: false\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>Simpan dan install dependency wiki.js</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo npm install</code></pre>\r\n<p>Tes untuk menjalankan wiki</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo node server</code></pre>\r\n<h1>Konfigurasi Service</h1>\r\n<p>Buat file konfigurasi service</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">nano /etc/systemd/system/wiki.service</code></pre>\r\n<p>File konfigurasi service</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">[Unit]\r\nDescription=Wiki.js\r\nAfter=network.target\r\n\r\n[Service]\r\nType=simple\r\nExecStart=/usr/bin/node server\r\nRestart=always\r\n# Consider creating a dedicated user for Wiki.js here:\r\nUser=root\r\n#Environment=NODE_ENV=production\r\nWorkingDirectory=/var/www/wiki\r\n\r\n[Install]\r\nWantedBy=multi-user.target</code></pre>\r\n<p>Reload systemd</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo systemctl daemon-reload</code></pre>\r\n<p>Jalankan service dan aktifkan service disaat booting</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo systemctl start wiki\r\nsudo systemctl enable wiki</code></pre>\r\n<h1>Konfigurasi Apache Webserver</h1>\r\n<p>Buat virtualhost wiki</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /etc/apache2/sites-available/wiki.conf</code></pre>\r\n<p>Virtualhost wiki</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;\r\n	ServerName wiki.kreasialamteknologi.com\r\n\r\n	ServerAdmin support@kreasialamteknologi.com\r\n	#DocumentRoot /var/www/wiki\r\n\r\n	ProxyRequests Off\r\n   		ProxyPreserveHost On\r\n   		ProxyVia Full\r\n   	&lt;Proxy *&gt;\r\n      	Require all granted\r\n   	&lt;/Proxy&gt;\r\n\r\n   	&lt;Location /&gt;\r\n      ProxyPass http://127.0.0.1:3300/\r\n      ProxyPassReverse http://127.0.0.1:3300/\r\n   	&lt;/Location&gt;\r\n\r\n	ErrorLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/error.log\r\n	CustomLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/access.log combined\r\n&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</code></pre>\r\n<p>Simpan dan aktifkan mod_proxy</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo a2enmod proxy\r\nsudo a2enmod proxy_http</code></pre>\r\n<p>Aktifkan virtualhost yang telah dibuat</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo a2ensite wiki</code></pre>\r\n<p>Restart apache</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo systemctl restart apache2</code></pre>\r\n<h1>Backup Wiki</h1>\r\n<p>Buat file dump file di folder wiki</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">mkdir /var/www/wiki/db/</code></pre>\r\n<p>Buat bash script untuk backup</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">nano /etc/backup_web.sh</code></pre>\r\n<p>Bash script backup</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">#Backup wiki\r\n#Backup DB \r\ndocker exec -it dbwordpress bash -c \"mysqldump -uroot -pKreasi123* wiki &gt; /home/backup/wiki_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql\"\r\n#Restart docker\r\ndocker restart dbwordpress\r\n#Copy to directory\r\ndocker cp dbwordpress:/home/backup/wiki_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql /var/www/wiki/db/\r\n#Delete file\r\nfind /var/www/wiki/db/*.sql -mtime +2 -exec rm {} \\;\r\n#To Directory\r\ncd /var/www/wiki/\r\n#Add, Commit and Push file\r\ngit add .\r\ngit commit -m \"wiki_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql\"\r\ngit push --set-upstream origin kat\r\n#Show completed\r\necho \"Completed\"</code></pre>\r\n<p>Simpan, dan lanjut konfigurasi crontab</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo crontab -e</code></pre>\r\n<p>Tambahkan di akhir file</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">0 5 * * * bash /etc/backup_web.sh</code></pre>\r\n','<h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"requirement\"><a href=\"#requirement\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> Requirement</h1><div>\n</div><ol>\n  <li>NodeJS</li>\n  <li>MariaDB</li>\n  <li>Apache Webserver</li>\n  <li>Certbot SSL</li>\n  <li>GIT</li>\n</ol><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"akses-wiki-kat\"><a href=\"#akses-wiki-kat\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> Akses Wiki KAT</h1><div>\n</div><figure class=\"table\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Domain</td>\n        <td>https://wiki.kreasialamteknologi.com</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Host</td>\n        <td>103.152.118.42</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>User</td>\n        <td>kreasialamteknologi</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Password</td>\n        <td>Kreasi123*</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Wiki Folder Path</td>\n        <td>/var/www/wiki</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Wiki Virtualhost Path</td>\n        <td>/etc/nginx/sites-available/wiki.conf</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</figure><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"install-wiki\"><a href=\"#install-wiki\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> Install Wiki</h1><div>\n</div><p>Masuk ke direktori dimana wiki akan ditempatkan</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Download wiki.js terbaru</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">wget https://github.com/Requarks/wiki/releases/download/2.5.214/wiki-js.tar.gz</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Ekstrak package</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">mkdir wiki\ntar xzf wiki-js.tar.gz -C ./wiki\ncd ./wiki</code></pre><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"konfigurasi-database-wiki\"><a href=\"#konfigurasi-database-wiki\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> Konfigurasi Database Wiki</h1><div>\n</div><figure class=\"table\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"2\">\n          <p style=\"text-align:center;\">Akses Database Wiki</p>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Database Type</td>\n        <td>MariaDB</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Host</td>\n        <td>103.152.118.42</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>User SSH</td>\n        <td>kreasialamteknologi</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Password SSH</td>\n        <td>Kreasi123*</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>User MariaDB</td>\n        <td>root</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Password MariaDB</td>\n        <td>Kreasi123*</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Port</td>\n        <td>3306</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Database Name</td>\n        <td>wiki</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Dump SQL Path</td>\n        <td>/var/www/wiki/db/</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</figure><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"menambah-database-wiki\"><a href=\"#menambah-database-wiki\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> Menambah Database Wiki</h2><div>\n</div><p>Akses ssh database wiki, kemudian masuk ke mariaDB</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mysql -h 103.152.118.42 -uroot -pKreasi123*</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Buat database wiki</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">create database wiki;</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Keluar dari mariaDB</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">exit</code></pre><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"konfigurasi-wiki\"><a href=\"#konfigurasi-wiki\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> Konfigurasi Wiki</h1><div>\n</div><p>Ganti nama file config.yml</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">mv config.sample.yml config.yml</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Edit konfigurasi wiki</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">nano config.yml</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Konfigurasi wiki, edit bagian port dan database wiki yang telah dibuat.</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"># ---------------------------------------------------------------------\n# Port the server should listen to\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nport: 3300 \n\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------\n# Database\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------\n# Supported Database Engines:\n# - postgres = PostgreSQL 9.5 or later\n# - mysql = MySQL 8.0 or later (5.7.8 partially supported, refer to docs)\n# - mariadb = MariaDB 10.2.7 or later\n# - mssql = MS SQL Server 2012 or later\n# - sqlite = SQLite 3.9 or later\n\ndb:\n  type: mariadb\n\n  # PostgreSQL / MySQL / MariaDB / MS SQL Server only:\n  host: localhost\n  port: 3306\n  user: root\n  pass: Kreasi123*\n  db: wiki\n  ssl: false\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Simpan dan install dependency wiki.js</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo npm install</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Tes untuk menjalankan wiki</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo node server</code></pre><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"konfigurasi-service\"><a href=\"#konfigurasi-service\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> Konfigurasi Service</h1><div>\n</div><p>Buat file konfigurasi service</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">nano /etc/systemd/system/wiki.service</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>File konfigurasi service</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">[Unit]\nDescription=Wiki.js\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nExecStart=/usr/bin/node server\nRestart=always\n# Consider creating a dedicated user for Wiki.js here:\nUser=root\n#Environment=NODE_ENV=production\nWorkingDirectory=/var/www/wiki\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Reload systemd</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo systemctl daemon-reload</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Jalankan service dan aktifkan service disaat booting</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo systemctl start wiki\nsudo systemctl enable wiki</code></pre><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"konfigurasi-apache-webserver\"><a href=\"#konfigurasi-apache-webserver\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> Konfigurasi Apache Webserver</h1><div>\n</div><p>Buat virtualhost wiki</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /etc/apache2/sites-available/wiki.conf</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Virtualhost wiki</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;\n	ServerName wiki.kreasialamteknologi.com\n\n	ServerAdmin support@kreasialamteknologi.com\n	#DocumentRoot /var/www/wiki\n\n	ProxyRequests Off\n   		ProxyPreserveHost On\n   		ProxyVia Full\n   	&lt;Proxy *&gt;\n      	Require all granted\n   	&lt;/Proxy&gt;\n\n   	&lt;Location /&gt;\n      ProxyPass http://127.0.0.1:3300/\n      ProxyPassReverse http://127.0.0.1:3300/\n   	&lt;/Location&gt;\n\n	ErrorLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/error.log\n	CustomLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/access.log combined\n&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Simpan dan aktifkan mod_proxy</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo a2enmod proxy\nsudo a2enmod proxy_http</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Aktifkan virtualhost yang telah dibuat</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo a2ensite wiki</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Restart apache</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo systemctl restart apache2</code></pre><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"backup-wiki\"><a href=\"#backup-wiki\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> Backup Wiki</h1><div>\n</div><p>Buat file dump file di folder wiki</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">mkdir /var/www/wiki/db/</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Buat bash script untuk backup</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">nano /etc/backup_web.sh</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Bash script backup</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">#Backup wiki\n#Backup DB \ndocker exec -it dbwordpress bash -c \"mysqldump -uroot -pKreasi123* wiki &gt; /home/backup/wiki_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql\"\n#Restart docker\ndocker restart dbwordpress\n#Copy to directory\ndocker cp dbwordpress:/home/backup/wiki_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql /var/www/wiki/db/\n#Delete file\nfind /var/www/wiki/db/*.sql -mtime +2 -exec rm {} \\;\n#To Directory\ncd /var/www/wiki/\n#Add, Commit and Push file\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"wiki_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql\"\ngit push --set-upstream origin kat\n#Show completed\necho \"Completed\"</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Simpan, dan lanjut konfigurasi crontab</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo crontab -e</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Tambahkan di akhir file</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">0 5 * * * bash /etc/backup_web.sh</code></pre><div>\n</div>','[{\"title\":\"Requirement\",\"anchor\":\"#requirement\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Akses Wiki KAT\",\"anchor\":\"#akses-wiki-kat\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Install Wiki\",\"anchor\":\"#install-wiki\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Konfigurasi Database Wiki\",\"anchor\":\"#konfigurasi-database-wiki\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"Menambah Database Wiki\",\"anchor\":\"#menambah-database-wiki\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"title\":\"Konfigurasi Wiki\",\"anchor\":\"#konfigurasi-wiki\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Konfigurasi Service\",\"anchor\":\"#konfigurasi-service\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Konfigurasi Apache Webserver\",\"anchor\":\"#konfigurasi-apache-webserver\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Backup Wiki\",\"anchor\":\"#backup-wiki\",\"children\":[]}]','html','2021-09-13T04:12:17.195Z','2021-09-13T14:08:38.894Z','ckeditor','en',3,3,'{\"js\":\"\",\"css\":\"\"}'),(16,'syspass','95038810e4a7e8f405a41db4e2d13cec9fa98eb4','Syspass Kreasi Alam Teknologi','Describe syspass KAT',0,1,NULL,'','','<h1>Requirement</h1>\n<ol>\n  <li>PHP</li>\n  <li>MariaDB</li>\n  <li>Apache Webserver</li>\n  <li>Certbot SSL</li>\n  <li>GIT</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>Akses Syspass KAT</h1>\n<figure class=\"table\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Domain</td>\n        <td>https://wiki.kreasialamteknologi.com</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Host</td>\n        <td>103.152.118.42</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>User</td>\n        <td>kreasialamteknologi</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Password</td>\n        <td>Kreasi123*</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Wiki Folder Path</td>\n        <td>/var/www/html/syspass</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Wiki Virtualhost Path</td>\n        <td>/etc/nginx/sites-available/syspass.conf</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>User Syspass</td>\n        <td>katsys</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Password Syspass</td>\n        <td>Bismillah123*</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</figure>\n<h1>Install Syspass</h1>\n<p>Buat direkrori syspass</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/www/html/syspass/</code></pre>\n<p>Download syspass repositori</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo git clone https://github.com/nuxsmin/sysPass.git  /var/www/html/syspass</code></pre>\n<p>Install composer, buat file \"<strong>install_composer.sh</strong>\"</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano install_composer.sh</code></pre>\n<p>File <strong>install_composer.sh</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">#!/bin/sh\nEXPECTED_SIGNATURE=\"$(wget -q -O - https://composer.github.io/installer.sig)\"\nphp -r \"copy(\'https://getcomposer.org/installer\', \'composer-setup.php\');\"\nACTUAL_SIGNATURE=\"$(php -r \"echo hash_file(\'sha384\', \'composer-setup.php\');\")\"\n\nif [ \"$EXPECTED_SIGNATURE\" != \"$ACTUAL_SIGNATURE\" ]\nthen\n    &gt;&amp;2 echo \'ERROR: Invalid installer signature\'\n    rm composer-setup.php\n    exit 1\nfi\n\nphp composer-setup.php --quiet\nRESULT=$?\nrm composer-setup.php\nexit $RESULT</code></pre>\n<p>Simpan, dan atur hak akses file <strong>install_composer.sh</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo chmod +x install_composer.sh</code></pre>\n<p>Jalankan bash script</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">\nsudo bash install_composer.sh</code></pre>\n<p>Setelah selesai, install sysPass dependencies</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">php composer.phar install --no-dev</code></pre>\n<h1>Konfigurasi Database Syspass</h1>\n<figure class=\"table\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"2\">\n          <p style=\"text-align:center;\">Akses Database Syspass</p>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Database Type</td>\n        <td>MariaDB</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Host</td>\n        <td>103.152.118.42</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>User SSH</td>\n        <td>kreasialamteknologi</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Password SSH</td>\n        <td>Kreasi123*</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>User MariaDB</td>\n        <td>root</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Password MariaDB</td>\n        <td>Kreasi123*</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Port</td>\n        <td>3306</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Database Name</td>\n        <td>sys</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Dump SQL Path</td>\n        <td>/var/www/html/syspass/db/</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</figure>\n<h2>Menambah Database Syspass</h2>\n<p>Akses ssh database wiki, kemudian masuk ke mariaDB</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mysql -h 103.152.118.42 -uroot -pKreasi123*</code></pre>\n<p>Buat database wiki</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">create database sys;</code></pre>\n<p>Keluar dari mariaDB</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">exit</code></pre>\n<h1>Konfigurasi Apache Webserver</h1>\n<p>Buat virtualhost wiki</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /etc/apache2/sites-available/syspass.conf</code></pre>\n<p>Virtualhost <strong>syspass.conf</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">RedirectMatch \"^/$\" \"/index.php\"\n\n&lt;Directory \"/var/www/html/syspass\"&gt;\n    DirectoryIndex index.php\n    Options -Indexes -FollowSymLinks -Includes -ExecCGI\n\n    &lt;RequireAny&gt;\n      Require expr \"%{REQUEST_URI} =~ m#.*/index\\.php(\\?r=)?#\"\n      Require expr \"%{REQUEST_URI} =~ m#.*/api\\.php$#\"\n      Require expr \"%{REQUEST_URI} =~ m#^/?$#\"\n    &lt;/RequireAny&gt;\n&lt;/Directory&gt;\n\n#&lt;Directory ~ \"/var/www/html/syspass.*/(css|js|images|fonts)\"&gt;\n#  Require all granted\n#&lt;/Directory&gt;\n\n&lt;FilesMatch \".(png|jpg|js|css|ttf|otf|eot|woff|woff2|ico)$\"&gt;\n    Require all granted\n&lt;/FilesMatch&gt;\n\n&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;\n	ServerName syspass.kreasialamteknologi.com\n\n	ServerAdmin support@kreasialamteknologi.com\n	DocumentRoot /var/www/html/syspass\n\n	ErrorLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/error.log\n	CustomLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/access.log combined\n&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</code></pre>\n<p>Simpan, dan aktifkan virtualhost yang telah dibuat</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo a2ensite syspass</code></pre>\n<p>Restart apache</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo systemctl restart apache2</code></pre>\n<h1>Konfigurasi Syspass</h1>\n<p>Buka URL \"<strong>syspass.kreasialamteknologi.com\"</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"/instalasi_1.png\">\n  <figcaption>Installation Page 1</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>Masukkan syspass admin user, password, dan master password</p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"/instalasi_2.png\">\n  <figcaption>Instalation Page 2</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>Masukkan konfigurasi database, sesuai database yang sudah dibuat. Pilih bahasa dan klik <strong>Install</strong></p>\n<p>Tunggu hingga instalasi selesai.</p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"/syspass_login.png\">\n  <figcaption>Syspass Login</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h1>Backup Syspass</h1>\n<p>Buat file dump file di folder wiki</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">mkdir /var/www/html/syspass/db/</code></pre>\n<p>Buat bash script untuk backup</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">nano /etc/backup_web.sh</code></pre>\n<p>Bash script backup</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">#Backup syspass\n#Backup DB \ndocker exec -it dbwordpress bash -c \"mysqldump -uroot -pKreasi123* sys &gt; /home/backup/syspass_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql\"\n#Restart docker\ndocker restart dbwordpress\n#Copy to directory\ndocker cp dbwordpress:/home/backup/syspass_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql /var/www/html/syspass/db/\n#Delete file\nfind /var/www/html/syspass/db/*.sql -mtime +2 -exec rm {} \\;\n#To Directory\ncd /var/www/html/syspass/\n#Add, Commit and Push file\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"syspass_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql\"\ngit push --set-upstream origin kat\n#Show completed\necho \"Completed\"</code></pre>\n<p>Simpan, dan lanjut konfigurasi crontab</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo crontab -e</code></pre>\n<p>Tambahkan di akhir file</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">0 5 * * * bash /etc/backup_web.sh</code></pre>\n','<h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"requirement\"><a href=\"#requirement\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> Requirement</h1><div>\n</div><ol>\n  <li>PHP</li>\n  <li>MariaDB</li>\n  <li>Apache Webserver</li>\n  <li>Certbot SSL</li>\n  <li>GIT</li>\n</ol><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"akses-syspass-kat\"><a href=\"#akses-syspass-kat\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¶</a> Akses Syspass KAT</h1><div>\n</div><figure class=\"table\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Domain</td>\n        <td>https://wiki.kreasialamteknologi.com</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Host</td>\n        <td>103.152.118.42</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>User</td>\n        <td>kreasialamteknologi</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Password</td>\n        <td>Kreasi123*</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>